        "description": "...Local Area Emergency affecting the Neighborhood of Avondale...\n\nThe following message is transmitted at the request of the Chicago Police Department.\n\nSuspicious person reported driving around the neighborhood of Avondale.\nMay be armed and dangerous. Do not approach suspicious vehicles or persons.\nThe suspect was driving north on Western Avenue near Diversey and Elston Avenue at 1255PM.\nIf you see a red sedan with tinted windows with Illinois license plate E C 3 5 4 1 9,\ncall 9 1 1 immediately.\nTEST MESSAGE\n\n&&\n\nLAT...LON 4194 8773 4194 8769 4193 8768 4193 8772\n\n$$\n\nCHICAGO NOTIFYME ALERTS",
